OL,3,CMan charged with murder following
OL,4,Cdeath of woman in Bracknell
OL,6,FA man has been charged with murder
OL,7,Ffollowing the death of a woman in
OL,8,FBracknell.
OL,10,FPolice officers were called on
OL,11,FWednesday 15 July to an address in
OL,12,FBirkdale following reports that a
OL,13,Fwoman had suffered a head injury,
OL,14,Fshortly before 7am.
OL,16,F40-year-old Natalie Clements was
OL,17,Fpronounced dead at the scene, despite
OL,18,Fthe best efforts of South Central
OL,19,FAmbulance Service.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/2
