OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784373493
OL,3,CMan charged with murder following
OL,4,Cdeath of woman in Bracknell
OL,6,FA Home Office post mortem examination
OL,7,Fhas now taken place, and concluded
OL,8,Fthat Natalie's death was caused by
OL,9,Fhead injuries.
OL,11,FThames Valley Police said her next of
OL,12,Fkin are being supported by specially
OL,13,Ftrained family liaison officers.
OL,15,FMatthew Robert Wilkie, aged 48, of
OL,16,FLiscombe, Bracknell has been charged
OL,17,Fwith one count of murder.
OL,19,FHe has been remanded into custody and
OL,20,Fis due to appear at Reading
OL,21,FMagistrates Court on Friday 17 July.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/2
